  "description": {
    "zh-CN": "《星露谷物语：扩展》是 ConcernedApe 原作的一款粉丝自制扩展 Mod。本 Mod 新增了 28 位 NPC、58 个地点、278 个角色事件、43 种鱼类，并对原版区域进行了重新构想，同时包含三张农场地图、一张反映所有变化的全新世界地图，以及新增的音乐、任务线、物品、作物、节日和大量其他内容！",
    "source": "Stardew Valley Expanded is a fanmade expansion for ConcernedApe's Stardew Valley. This mod adds 28 new NPCs,  58 locations, 278 character events, 43 fish, reimagined vanilla areas, three farm maps, a reimagined world map reflecting all changes, new music, questlines, objects, crops, festivals, and many miscellaneous additions!"
  },
